{
  "stem": "935.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then one of the guards, who had perhaps bad night, or no night at all, would say, every second, every fourth, every five, out, into the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Which means you never knew where to stand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Or the whole row, or only the first row, or only the third.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You played musical chairs all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But these were the things in between which happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was in a block.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was the-- 30,000 from the famous, famous-- I mean, I did know about it before.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Bensberg, a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There were only a few hundred in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The rest went up in flames.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] What went on in the camp, in the barracks itself-- you hid under thin blankets full of lice.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You fought for blankets full of lice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There was never any light.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was always dark, because there were practically no light and no windows.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There were many, many, many, much too many people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "What you got was stupid coffee, which wasn't coffee, and bread which the blockova or the blockalteste stole anyway from you, and exchanged against ration in the other camp, in the nicer camp, where the girls were, the political were, or the non-Jews were.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We had a blockova, Ilse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She was a lesbian from Berlin, 22-year-old, a real butch, who stole our ration, and then exchanged it in the other camp to buy herself some girlfriends.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then she had an assistant, which was 26-year-old Katja from Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "A former professor in university, spoke five languages, was totally mad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Ilsa never hit, she just didn't want to stay in this camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "She just spent most of her time in the other camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "She let Katja do this.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
